Bouldering at APEX.description: Are you an over achiever? Do you like challenges? Do you like solving puzzles? Are you jealous of montain goats? If you answered "yes" to one or more of these questions, join us for a fun bouldering evening at APEX!

It is time for a little competition, battles from friends to friends, mentor to mentee. Invite all of your friends for a tournament of a short, quick version of the most popular sport in the world. 
It is time for a futsal tournament⚽⚽!!!
